OL,3,CDan Walker's former co-host withdraws
OL,4,C'bullying' claims as agreement reached
OL,6,FPresenter Claudia`Liza Vanderpuije has
OL,7,Fwithdrawn claims against her former
OL,8,FChannel 5 News co-host Dan Walker
OL,9,Fafter reaching a "mutual agreement"
OL,10,Fwith the company and ITN.
OL,12,FVanderpuije, who co-hosted a show with
OL,13,FWalker for a year between 2022 and
OL,14,F2023, had filed claims of unfair
OL,15,Fdismissal, discrimination and
OL,16,Fharassment against ITN and Channel 5's
OL,17,Fowner, Paramount, on grounds of race
OL,18,Fand sex, and breach of contract.
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@cO]
