OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777100755
OL,3,CDan Walker's former co-host withdraws
OL,4,C'bullying' claims as agreement reached
OL,6,FWalker, a former BBC Breakfast host
OL,7,Fand Strictly Come Dancing contestant,
OL,8,Fwas listed as a respondent in the
OL,9,Fclaims alongside Channel 5 and ITN `
OL,10,Fincluding ITN CEO Rachel Corp ` and
OL,11,FParamount Global, which owns Channel 5.
OL,13,FThe case was to be heard at a London
OL,14,Femployment tribunal from Monday, and
OL,15,FWalker, 49, was due to appear later
OL,16,Fduring the proceedings.
OL,18,FBut speaking at the London Tribunals
OL,19,FCentre on Friday, Judge Emma Webster
OL,20,Fsaid she would dismiss all claims
OL,21,Fahead of the tribunal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
