OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777100755
OL,3,CDan Walker's former co-host withdraws
OL,4,C'bullying' claims as agreement reached
OL,6,FA statement from Vanderpuije's lawyers
OL,7,Fsaid: "Claudia-Liza Vanderpuije can
OL,8,Fconfirm that a mutual agreement has
OL,9,Fbeen reached with ITN and Channel 5 in
OL,10,Frespect of the matters subject to
OL,11,Ftribunal proceedings.
OL,13,F"Claudia-Liza fully withdraws her
OL,14,Fallegations relating to Dan Walker and
OL,15,Fdoes not intend to repeat or pursue
OL,16,Fthem."
OL,18,FIt is understood that an internal
OL,19,Finvestigation into claims against
OL,20,FWalker was not upheld, and no
OL,21,Fmisconduct was found.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOUxD@FO]
