OL,3,CDan Walker's former co-host withdraws
OL,4,C'bullying' claims as agreement reached
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWriting on his social media pages,
OL,12,FWalker said: "Channel 5 and ITN have
OL,13,Freached an agreement with the
OL,14,Fclaimant. I firmly feel that I should
OL,15,Fnever have been pulled into this;
OL,16,Fhowever, I was fully prepared to go to
OL,17,Ftribunal and defend the allegations
OL,18,Fwhich were levelled at me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
