OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777100755
OL,3,CDan Walker's former co-host withdraws
OL,4,C'bullying' claims as agreement reached
OL,6,F"Through all of this, I have always
OL,7,Fbeen concerned for the claimant's
OL,8,Fwellbeing, and that has not changed. I
OL,9,Fhope she finds peace.
OL,11,F"I want to thank my family and friends
OL,12,Ffor all their love and support through
OL,13,Fthis. I will be forever grateful to
OL,14,Fthose who were kind enough to go on
OL,15,Fthe record with their accounts of
OL,16,Fworking alongside me.
OL,18,F"My thanks also to my legal team and
OL,19,Fthe wonderful colleagues at 5 News and
OL,20,FClassic FM who have supported me every
OL,21,Fstep of the way."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
