OL,3,CDan Walker's former co-host withdraws
OL,4,C'bullying' claims as agreement reached
OL,6,FA spokesperson for ITN said: "We
OL,7,Fcontinue to deny these claims in full,
OL,8,Fand we are glad this matter has been
OL,9,Fresolved."
OL,11,FA Channel 5 spokesperson said: "We
OL,12,Fstrongly reject the claims that were
OL,13,Fmade and are pleased that this matter
OL,14,Fhas been resolved and that all the
OL,15,Fallegations relating to Dan Walker
OL,16,Fhave been withdrawn."
